title: Fredrik Claesson scores winner, Binghamton beats St. John's 5-4 in OT (NHL - National Hockey ...
text: ( Source : NHL - National Hockey League ) ST. JOHN' S, N .L. - Fredrik Claesson scored 1:35 into overtime as the Binghamton Senators edged the host St. John's IceCaps 5-4 on Tuesday in American Hockey League action. Matt Puempel , Travis Ewanyk,
